  <h2>Limitation of Liability</h2>
  <p>Sharp Picks provides information on an "as is" basis. We do not guarantee the accuracy, completeness, or reliability of any analysis. Sharp Picks is not liable for any direct, indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from the use of our product, including but not limited to financial losses from wagering activity.</p>

