  <div class="callout callout-warn">Refunds are not issued based on betting outcomes, pick frequency, or the number of pass days. The Sharp Picks model is designed to be selective. Extended periods without a published pick are a normal and expected part of the product. By subscribing, you acknowledge that pass days are part of the product's value, not an absence of service.</div>

